Output public/gifs/05_config.gif
Set FontSize 12
Set Width 800
Set Height 1100
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Framerate 24
Set WaitTimeout 10s

Sleep 1s
Type "mosaic config --unpaywall-email username@affiliation.xyz"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Wait
Sleep 1s
Type "mosaic config --show"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Wait
Sleep 8s
